  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg width=\"1190\" height=\"658\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/absolvement-sin-tier-list-and-guide-e1747408187691.png?fit=1190%2C658\" alt=\"Cover image of Absolvement Roblox experience with the best Sins in front of it.\" fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\tImage by The Escapist\t\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\tOnly brave go with the Abomination...\t\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv id=\"wp-block-gamurs-article-metadata-1027581\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e|\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp id=\"wp-block-gamurs-article-metadata__date-and-time__published__1027581\" data-datetime=\"May 16, 2025 11:06 am UTC-4\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPublished: May 16, 2025 11:06 am\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\u003cp data-characters=\"348\" data-injectable=\"true\" data-video=\"true\"\u003eChoosing the right Sins when creating a new character in Absolvement is as crucial as choosing your race, because you won’t be able to change them. However, with each of them sounding worse than the other, making that choice can be difficult. To help you pick only the best Sins available, we prepared the following \u003cstrong\u003eAbsolvement Sin tier list\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n    \u003cdiv data-current-count=\"0\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"table-of-contents\"\u003eTable of Contents\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"#h-absolvement-sin-tier-list\" data-level=\"2\"\u003eAbsolvement Sin Tier List\u003c/a\u003e